<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<p></p>



<p style="font-size:19px"><em>"We would like to extend our sincere gratitude to our amazing Mayo Clinic residents and fellows who give of their time and compassionate services to the patients in our Sulzbacher clinics. The weekly 'Mayo Learners Clinic' is a blessing to Sulzbacher, the vulnerable patients that we serve and to the community at large. If it were not for you, these patients might not receive the treatment that they need and would end up even more ill and in an emergency room or worse. Thank you, Mayo residents and fellows, for your critical partnership, service and empathy. We appreciate you more than you know."</em></p>



<p style="font-size:19px">Cindy Funkhouser, president and CEO<br>Sulzbacher Center, Jacksonville, Fla.</p>
