<p class="has-medium-font-size">Patient by patient, researchers at Mayo Clinic's Center for Individualized Medicine&amp;nbsp;are making notable progress in rare disease diagnostics and treatments. <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/advancing-rare-disease-breakthroughs-with-genomics-ai-and-innovation/">Read more</a>.</p>
